---
title: "Is Co-Fermentation Cheating? Wrong Question."
date: "2026-04-02"
description: "The specialty coffee world is split on whether co-fermented coffee belongs in competition. The more useful question is what processing transparency should require from everyone else."
tags: ["coffee", "supply-chain", "data", "market-intelligence"]
pillar: "supply-chain"
